data.description: This adorable 3 Bed 2 Bath home is one of a kind. Don't miss out on the best location in the Siena neighborhood!! This house is directly across the street from the neighborhood pond & pool with no neighbors across the street! Also walk to the playground, basketball court, covered pavilion with tables or fish in the lake across from your house! This home offers a large master suite with garden tub, separate shower & a huge 5x12 walk-in closet with built-ins! With an open floor plan & large living room, great kitchen & stainless steel appliances! This home is perfect for entertaining. Refrigerator will Stay! Don't miss out on this beautiful property!
